up and go.

\SE[4]Daddy. You didn't forget your bento today, did you?

I told you countless times, didn't I? You almost forgot and
rushed out.

Are you going out with Aisha-chan today? Shouldn't you go pick
her up soon?

\SE[5]Wait for me! I'll be right there!

By the way, could you also bring back some Merukuru Grass? It's
the best for shoulder stiffness and lower back pain. I think it
grows deep in the hunting grounds during this season.

grounds, right....

Today, I'm going hunting with Aisha. It's dangerous for you to
engage in combat, so stay on guard. \SE[0] Today is guard duty
for you.
I feel like I'm being stared at sadly by a stuffed animal...
\SE[14]Ugh... Even if you make that face... \SE[33]Ugh... Grrr...
I decided to bring a stuffed animal with me!
